        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_PRO/Scenes/Missions/CoastalTown/scene_ebola.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 8f8c2be2-d99c-4a71-89df-2e3ee4a77fa0).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47.  Your next target is that of Salvatore Bravuomo. Our Client(s) has asked us to do a quick favor for that of the family of a murder victim. John Sheppard was on trial for the murder of another tourist in Sapienza. He was able to get away with murder from non-other than Salvatore, the infamous lawyer of Sapienza and owns an office in the town at city hall. They want him to die the same way the tourist was murdered 10 years ago. Get to hunting 47, and don&apos;t leave evidence behind.",
